definition: lit. earthen steps and a small cottage/frugal living conditions (idiom)

sentences.english: Forth from thy hovel door thou Ethiopia com ist to me.
sentences.chinese: 你埃塞俄比亞人，從你的茅屋的門裏走出，向我走近。

sentences.english: At the last blow the hut disappeared, and before him stood the little princess .
sentences.chinese: 最後一擊時，小茅屋消失了，而小公主就站在他前面。

sentences.english: Love lives in cottages as well as in courts.
End to end cottage, this study Canxia.
sentences.chinese: 終須結茅屋，到此學餐霞。

sentences.english: The daughter cooked, cleaned the hut, and took care of the baby.
sentences.chinese: 女兒則燒飯煮菜，打掃茅屋和照顧小孩。

sentences.english: In their plaited hut there is nothing but health and love.
sentences.chinese: 在他們的小茅屋裏只有健康和愛。

sentences.english: We are Amphitryon of the JACAL .
Is it easy to get a Jacal?
sentences.chinese: 得到一個小茅屋容易嗎？

sentences.english: She rushed out of the hut when she heard her dappled cow low in dismay.
sentences.chinese: 聽到小花牛驚慌的哞哞低鳴，她快步跑出茅屋。

sentences.english: When he was leaving, he saw Finola at the door of the hut, and saw that she was crying.
sentences.chinese: 離去時，他看到菲諾拉站在茅屋的門口哭泣。

sentences.english: There was a month's rent on their little home which he had to pay.
sentences.chinese: 這小茅屋還有一個月的租金他必須付。

sentences.english: She lived deep in the forest in a tiny cottage and sold herbal remedies for a living.
sentences.chinese: 她住在森林深處的一間小茅屋裏，以賣草藥維生。

sentences.english: "Cottage cheese provides two different types of protein: whey and casein, " Carlucci says.
sentences.chinese: 茅屋芝士提供兩種蛋白質，乳清和乾酪素。

sentences.english: The hut by the side of the water is shaded by an overhanging tree.
sentences.chinese: 水邊的茅屋被懸於頭頂的大樹廕庇着。

sentences.english: Love can turn the cottage into a golden palace.
sentences.chinese: 愛情可使茅屋變成金碧輝煌的宮殿。

sentences.english: The old man knocked up a hut for mountain - climbers.
sentences.chinese: 那位老人給爬山者草草地搭成一小茅屋。

definition: lit. woodcutter's family/humble background/poor family background
a room in a Buddhist monastery/a temple
